window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Dr. Brian Miller, a physicist, is investigating what might be a buried ship along with the military and NASA. During the investigation, he accidentally triggers a time-travel mechanism designed for ultra-long-distance communications.&nbsp;</p> <p>He discovers he's landed in his 18-year-old body, but the original occupant is still present.</p>"; 
